title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Also found on the web was this nugget: thebesttranslator@hotmail.com wrote: Dear List Members, I am The BEST TRANSLATOR ever been. To which one of the put-upon list members replied, “Not into English, you're not.” [Submitted by Juliette Shapiro.]
